  "texts": [
    "The study comprised four steps: image preprocessing with a median filter, segmentation using the k-means clustering algorithm, kidney stone detection, and classification.",
    "The team gathered data from approximately 40 patients diagnosed with kidney stone diseases, utilizing CT scans in a clinical setting.",
    "The novel approach in this study aimed to detect boundaries and segment areas and enhance kidney stone detection through pixel-level analysis.",
    "This methodology enables both the localization of kidney stones and the quantification of affected patients.",
    "The algorithm achieved an accuracy rate of 92.5%."
  ],
